\begin_layout Section
Introduction
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Thank you for picking up a copy of Armoured Warfare Simulator 2014, an online,
 multiplayer game where blowing up as many tanks as possible is your ultimate
 goal.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This client is the game end of the system, you boot up 
\series bold
aws.py 
\series default
and have fun racking up damage against friends or people online.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
Installation Instructions
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Installation for UNIX-like Systems
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
All this game requires is a sane python 2.7 environment, test this by entering
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset listings
inline false
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$ python -V
\end_layout

\end_inset

into your terminal.
 If it returns 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

Python 2.7.[anything]
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 you are good to run this game without installation.
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash

\backslash

\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
If not, use your package manager to install python 2.7 and continue.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
You can now use the following commands to run the game:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset listings
inline false
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$ tar vxf AWS-x.x.x.tar.gz
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$ cd /path/to/game/directory/
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$ python aws.py
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
This will start up the game, follow the on-screen instructions to continue.
\end_layout

